FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_info mi
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.production_year  <  2002 AND ci.person_id  >  1867057 AND ci.role_id  >  3 AND mi.info_type_id  =  3
